Clean Architecture Layers
domain/          ← Entities, Interfaces, Errors, Enums (no dependencies)
application/     ← Use Cases, DTOs, Validators, Mappers
infrastructure/  ← MongoDB, Redis, Email, Services (implements domain interfaces)
interfaces/      ← Controllers, Routes, Middleware, HTTP Validators (Zod)
shared/          ← Logger, Config, Constants, Utils

